                <h3><a class="anchor" id="top" name="parlourplayers"></a>Parlour Players present "Season's Greetings" on 8/9/10 November</h3>
                <p>Thursday 8, Friday 9 and Saturday 10 November 2018, 7:45pm in Sanderstead United Reformed Church Hall</p>
                <p>Tickets £9 To book your tickets go to www.parlourplayers.co.uk and click on the TicketSource link or phone the Box Office on 020 8657 2632. Alternatively, <%= link_to "post the slip on this form", "resource/SG_PCS_Wording.pdf" %> to The Parlour Players Box Office 25 Farm Fields, Sanderstead CR2 0HQ.</p>
                </p>
              </td>
              <td class="events">
