                <p>Come along to the Gruffy to see the illunination of Sanderstead with the switching on of the Christmas lights by a famous celebrity. Join in Christmas carol singing led by the All Saints' choir. The lights and Christmas trees are provided by donations from the Sanderstead Residents' Association and our local Councillors.</p>
